Summary: Saw a stationary sphere that was reflecting the colors of the sky
trends: There have been 5 other sightings in Lakeville
There were no other sightings in Lakeville on or around April 3rd 2013
divs: Sighting DetailsThe witness was travelling on 35W-S and exited on 175th St in Lakeville, MN She saw a sphere that appeared oval shaped hovering above the tree line. It remained stationary. It was reflecting the colors of the sky. One could see the edges of the sphere, then a transparent area, then the color of the morning sky. The object was viewed through the windshield of the car. She had the feeling that the object was under intelligent control. She remembers feeling very nervous and "Not now. I have to get to work"
